{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_13_01",
  "title": "鈴村優 1話 生徒会長になります！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "（前に、瑠依ちゃんが、ふいに聞いてきたことがある）\n（きっと、瑠依ちゃんは覚えてへんかもしれんけど――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Once‚ Rui-chan suddenly asked me something.）\n（She might not even remember it now‚ though—）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ優、私、気になっているんだけど……\n……学校に行く意味って、何かしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Yu‚ there’s something I’ve been wondering…\n…What’s the point of going to school?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4494.081783299998,
          "startTime": 19.36074845
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.11074845
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.11074845
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.2940798759
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、聞いて！\nうち、生徒会長になります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan‚ listen!\nI’m going to become the student council president!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.2940798759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.5607465426
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……？　えーっと……優？　どういうこと？\n突然二年生の教室まで来て……生徒会長になる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…? Um… Yu? What do you mean?\nYou suddenly came to a second-year classroom… and you’re becoming president?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.2666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.2668465614
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "そう、生徒会長や！\nうちの野望を聞いてほしくて、飛んできたんやで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep‚ student council president!\nI rushed over‚ cause I wanted to tell you my big dream!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8001798947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.5335132281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "や、野望……？\n優、分かるように説明して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-big dream…?\nYu‚ explain it so I can understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2999996185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.0657131195
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "さっきHRで『生徒会長さんの転校が急に決まったから\n生徒会長選挙を来月頭にやる』って聞いてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In homeroom just now‚ they said‚ “Since the student council president is\nsuddenly transferring‚ we’ll hold a new election at the start of next month.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4657166798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.6323833465
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、それは私も聞いたわ\n確か今の会長は進学コースの三年生だったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I heard that too.\nThe current president is a third-year in the academic track‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4999996185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.1239257176
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、うちら芸能コースやし学年もちゃうけど\n廊下ですれ違ったら挨拶してくれて、ええ人やった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ we’re in the performing arts course and different grades‚\nbut they always greeted us in the hallway. Such a nice person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.1905923843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.657259051
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "そんな生徒会長さんの後を継ぎたい……\nうち、そう思ったんよ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to follow in their footsteps…\nThat’s what I thought…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.457259051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.2905923843
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったの。なんだかちょっとわざとらしいけど……\nまぁいいわ。でも、優はまだ一年生よね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. It sounds a bit dramatic‚ though…\nWell‚ fine. But you’re still a first-year‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.0333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.2795951207
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "一年生が生徒会長になったらあかんって校則はないんよ\n生徒手帳も全部読んだし、職員室でも確認してきたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no rule saying a first-year can’t be president.\nI read the whole handbook and even checked with the staff room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1795951207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.9462617874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "でも……いえ、はっきり聞くわ\nアイドル活動はどうするつもり？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… no‚ I’ll ask directly.\nWhat about your idol activities?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.9126114209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、そっちも手を抜いたりしません\n次のライブも近いしな。選挙活動中もちゃんとやります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I won’t slack off there either.\nThe next live is coming up‚ but I’ll handle both properly—even during campaigning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.4126114209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.9126114209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……でも、もしそれで当選したら\nなおさら学校生活が忙しくなるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… but if you actually win‚\nyour school life will get even busier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.9333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.2604999224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました\n瑠依ちゃんにはほんまの理由、ちゃんと言います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Alright.\nI’ll tell you the real reason‚ Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.4604999224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.7604999224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "理由……？\n立候補する、他の理由があるっていうの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason…?\nYou have another reason for running?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.9999965667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.5021781921
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "あんな、うち今『恋の校則はままならない』略して\n『ここまま』って少女漫画にハマっとってな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ right now I’m hooked on a manga called\n“The Rules of Love Don’t Go as Planned‚” or “Kokomama” for short!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.0688448588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.5688397725
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "『ここまま』は、生徒会長であるヒロインが\n番長ひきいる不良だらけの学校で活躍する漫画なんや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In “Kokomama‚” the heroine is the student council president\nwho shines in a school full of delinquents led by a school gang leader!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.7688397725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "授業にも出ず、たまり場で過ごす番長を説得するのに\nヤンキーの巣窟に一人乗り込む生徒会長！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To convince the school gang leader who skips class and hangs out all day‚\nshe storms into their den all by herself!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.0355064392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.8355166118
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "光る眼鏡！　揺れるおさげ！\n伸びた背筋に、きらめくセーラー襟！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shining glasses! Swaying braids!\nA straight posture and a sparkling sailor collar!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.2355166118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.3688448589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_01-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "番長はな、昔気質で女に手を上げへんのが信条なんや\nそれを誰よりも理解しとるのが、生徒会長でな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The gang leader is old-fashioned and never raises a hand against girls!\nAnd the one who understands him best is the president!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.5021781922,
